%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-thi%E1%BB%81n-kinh/poem-tuxu4iLcF3xnXyRsWnEiqA">Thần nghệ Siêu Sư viện độc thiền kinh - 晨詣超師院讀禪經</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADn-h%C3%A0nh-vi%E1%BB%85n-tu-thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng/poem-GtdmSoi6EuIHKcwHFkRN8g">Tín hành viễn tu thuỷ đồng - 信行遠修水筒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ph%C3%BA-L%E1%BB%99c-b%C3%A1t-c%E1%BA%A3nh-k%E1%BB%B3-3-H%C6%B0ng-B%C3%ACnh-nguy%C3%AAn/poem-SCAe5hSUbv2bfvMFefrTxg">Vịnh Phú Lộc bát cảnh kỳ 3 - Hưng Bình nguyên - 詠富祿八景其三－興瓶源</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-C%C3%B4ng-Ch%C3%ADnh/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Th%C3%A1i-B%C3%ACnh-phong-c%E1%BA%A3nh-thi/poem-FEw-zDq3ZNVIPhCSNzwLKw">Vịnh Thái Bình phong cảnh thi - 詠太平風景詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-C%C3%B4ng-Ch%C3%ADnh/author-SDV6tYF_Wcqz2LjLwuXPyg">Đào Công Chính</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Dng-nh%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2y-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-l%C4%83ng-t%E1%BA%B1ng-t%E1%BB%A7ng-x%E1%BB%A9-t%C3%B4n/poem-joqJTHP6-4swIj_Bsy2e5Q">Vọng nhạc (Tây Nhạc lăng tằng tủng xứ tôn) - 望嶽（西嶽崚嶒竦處尊）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
